name: Banzai Pipeline
description:
Banzai Pipeline encapsulates the human quest for peak experience. A metaphor borrowed from the surfing world, surfing the Pipeline takes courage and instinct. It is a thing of inspiration and a symbol of the mighty power of nature.

The wave rises and grows in size and beauty. It's a living sculpture, a moving picture. It's a challenge, a mystery, an impenetrable wall of water that will test your courage and instincts.

There is a paradox in surfing. The surfer who rides the mighty wave might not be the best in the world. The best in the world might be busy looking at crypto art.
